Document: GDScriptSyntaxHighlighter
Path: godot/classes/class_gdscriptsyntaxhighlighter.rst
Summary: GDScript syntax highlighter used to color-code GDScript code in the editor

GDScriptSyntaxHighlighter inherits from EditorSyntaxHighlighter < SyntaxHighlighter < Reference. This class provides syntax highlighting functionality for GDScript in the Godot editor, applying color-coding to different language elements for improved code readability and editing experience.
